  "timeout": 30,
  "retry_count": 3,
  "options": {}
}
</tool_call>

Since the network_fetcher timed out, I'll try again with a shorter timeout value to see if we can get a response more quickly.

<tool_call>network_fetcher
{
  "source": "https://api.example.com/data",
